@Iam.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5288
@Gateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5057
@Test_User_Id = d1cd3b1e-b8cc-4d37-8f55-09ad18b76c5f
@DevSeed_Email = dev.seed@sync.local
@DevSeed_Password = Sync@12345
@DevSeed_DeviceId = dev-seed-device-001

### Dev login (IamSeedData.IamDbSeeder on IAM.API startup — password Sync@12345)
#   demo@sync.local      — User
#   admin@sync.local     — SystemAdmin
#   partner@sync.local   — Partner
#   dev.seed@sync.local  — User
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{DevSeed_Email}}",
  "password": "{{DevSeed_Password}}",
  "deviceId": "{{DevSeed_DeviceId}}",
  "platform": "Android"
}

###

### Step 1: Save Basic Info (Onboarding Step 1)
POST {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/biometrics/onboarding/basic
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{Test_User_Id}}

{
  "gender": "Male",
  "dateOfBirth": "1995-05-15",
  "heightCm": 175.0
}

### Step 2: Save Goals & Activity (Onboarding Step 2 - Triggers BMR, TDEE & Macros)
POST {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/biometrics/onboarding/goals
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{Test_User_Id}}

{
  "currentWeightKg": 75.0,
  "targetWeightKg": 70.0,
  "fitnessGoal": "LoseFat",
  "activityLevel": "ModeratelyActive",
  "fitnessExperienceLevel": "Intermediate",
  "workoutLocationPreference": "Gym"
}

### Step 3: Save Body Composition (Onboarding Step 3 - Optional)
POST {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/biometrics/onboarding/composition
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{Test_User_Id}}

{
  "currentBodyFatPercentage": 18.5,
  "goalBodyFatPercentage": 12.0,
  "muscleMassKg": 35.2
}

### Step 4: Save Safeguards (Onboarding Step 4 - Optional)
POST {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/biometrics/onboarding/safeguards
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{Test_User_Id}}

{
  "injuries": [
    "Lower back stiffness",
    "Left shoulder impingement"
  ],
  "medications": [
    "None"
  ]
}

### Step 5: Get Full Biometric Profile
GET {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/biometrics
X-User-Id: {{Test_User_Id}}
@UserId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### View profile + preferences (InfoProfile & Preferences)
GET {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/me/profile-settings
Accept: application/json
X-User-Id: {{UserId}}

###

### View vouchers + achievements inventory
GET {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/me/inventory
Accept: application/json
X-User-Id: {{UserId}}

###

### Update basic account display fields
PUT {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/me/basic-profile
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{UserId}}

{
  "fullName": "Nguyen Van A",
  "avatarUrl": "https://cdn.example/avatars/a.png",
  "preferredLanguage": "vi",
  "timeZone": "Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh"
}

###

### Create / update fitness (biometric) profile
PUT {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/me/fitness-profile
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{UserId}}

{
  "gender": "Male",
  "dateOfBirth": "2000-01-15",
  "heightCm": 175,
  "currentWeightKg": 72,
  "targetWeightKg": 68,
  "fitnessGoal": "LoseFat",
  "activityLevel": "ModeratelyActive",
  "fitnessExperienceLevel": "Beginner",
  "workoutLocationPreference": "Gym",
  "injuries": [],
  "medications": []
}

###

### Setup account preferences (UserPreference)
PUT {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/me/account-preferences
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{UserId}}

{
  "agentPersona": "FriendlyBuddy",
  "motivationStyle": "Supportive",
  "autoOrderEnabled": false,
  "dataSharingConsent": true,
  "marketingConsent": false,
  "favoriteFoods": ["chicken", "rice"],
  "dislikedFoods": ["liver"],
  "allergies": [
    { "allergenName": "peanut", "severity": "high", "notes": null }
  ]
}

### Step 6: Log New Weight (Triggers recalculation)
HttpPatch {{Iam.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/biometrics/weight
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{Test_User_Id}}

{
  "currentWeightKg": 74.2
}

